item.description:
Venez chez moi (c'est Jenny qui parle) to lovely Atlantic Heights pour le Poisson d'Avril! Bring a dish of your choice for the usual potluck-type gathering and come on over! Please RSVP and let me know (in the Comments field of the RSVP) what delicious food item you plan to bring.

Merci bien, and see you all on April Fool's Day!!

Jenny lives in Portsmouth. Please RSVP to receive her contact info and driving directions!
